title: Cowboys' DeMarcus Lawrence Helps Supply Meals to First Responders Amid COVID-19
description: Dallas Cowboys  defensive end DeMarcus Lawrence enlisted the help of teammates Jaylon Smith and Daniel Ross as well as local food-truck owners to help support Dallas first responders who are currently dealing with the coronavirus pandemic...
